CRM Consultant/CRM Business Analyst - 6-12 month contract London London, UK - Market Contract (CRM Analyst, CRM Consultant, Functional analyst, CRM business analyst, Customer Relationship Management).
My client are currently undergoing a digital transformation project. Central to this project is their use of CRM. They currently have Microsoft Dynamics which they are using at their CRM tool.
They need a CRM consultant who is able to come in and speak to the stake holders and users and engage them in such a way as to make recommendation and improvements on how to improve their use of CRM and get the benefits of CRM, and better understand, utilise and make recommendations to them on how they can better use the functionality available within the CRM Dynamics system and to better use CRM to improve their Sales and also to some extent Marketing.
Candidates with experience of MS Dynamics and understanding would be a plus but is not essential.
Office Location is London (but candidate could be based out of Birmingham office)
Please send CV in first instance to be considered
